        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Esthesia",
          "data": "Ha ! This is the place of my dreams, everything sounds so wonderful !"
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-angelTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "Well, for us it is an important sanctuary. We watch over it as guardians."
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-esthesiaTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Esthesia",
          "data": "The inhabitants too are made of crystal! How lucky you are to live here."
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-angelTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "Yes, everything is made of vibrating matter. Even our names! The Z often comes back from around here!"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "As you have felt, this place is a hotbed of elemental vibrations, and we make sure that nothing distracts it from its balance."
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-esthesiaTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Esthesia",
          "data": "It really has nothing to do with where I come from."
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-angelTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "I know the Earth well too. I had tried to restore the balance, but my powers were soon exhausted."
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "However, I was able to understand the causes of this imbalance, I counted three that must be familiar to you."
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "First of all, I was able to observe the dissonances produced by all kinds of mechanical machines."
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "And again, at other times, artificial lights that oscillate at a frenetic pace."
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "And finally stressed earthlings, who unknowingly communicate their nerve waves."
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-esthesiaTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Esthesia",
          "data": "Ah ! All this speaks to me a lot ! Does my hypersensitivity have to do with these vibrations ?"
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-angelTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "Yes, but I don't have the power to change that. However, I do want to help you, and maybe in another way."
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Angel",
          "data": "I propose to accompany you wherever you go. I can perceive the dissonances in the environment, I will always know how to guide you on the calmest path."
        },
		{
          "type": "image",
		  "metadata": "background",
          "data": "cutscene 1920\\cutscene08-esthesiaTalking"
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "metadata": "Esthesia",
          "data": "Does this mean ... that I will once again have the power to move around the city as I want ?"
        }
      ]
